	  (1.64): Added Send Message formatting for HamHUD 20-character
	  display.

2006-08-25 22:33  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.577), src/messages.c (1.67), src/messages.h (1.22),
	  src/messages_gui.c (1.63): Adding error messages to the Send
	  Message dialog.  Fixing directed queries.  Adding D7A and D700 input
	  modes to the Send Message dialog.  Fixed a long message bug so
	  67-char messages can now be sent.

2006-08-25 22:24  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.216), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.205), config/language-French.sys (1.206),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.213), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.206), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.203),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.213): Adding some warning messages
	  for the Send Message dialog.

