2006-08-23 12:17  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.713): Moving reload_object_item() and
	  Restore_CAD_Objects_from_file() from main() up into UpdateTime().
	  This is so that the image can be created and the global map corner
	  variables updates first.  Points were getting rejected on loading
	  because these variables were not initialized yet.

