2006-08-21 13:33  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.573): A fix for bug #1474401, where an auto-answer or
	  some other message to us which doesn't have a message-ID ends up
	  showing up in a Group Message dialog.  This fix makes them appear in
	  a Send Message dialog, plus we refuse to ack them which is correct
	  behavior.

