2006-08-07 13:37  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.487): Adding clipt(), clip2d(), clipt_long(), and
	  clip2d_long() functions.  These are implementations of the
	  Liang/Barsky/Slater line-clipping algorithm.  Modified draw_vector()
	  and draw_vector_ll() to use them.  Changing cutoff points for
	  points/vectors to be consistent (+/-16000).

