	  least of reasonable size.

2006-08-02 15:26  we7u

	* src/util.c (1.212): The chdir() call in log_data() appears to
	  corrupt our "file" parameter.  We don't appear to need the chdir()
	  function call anyway, so have commented it out.  We get passed the
	  complete root-anchored path/filename as-is.

