	* src/objects.c (1.40): Changed/added some comments.  No code
	  changes.

2006-08-02 11:53  we7u

	* src/objects.c (1.39): Backing out the update of the Edit & Delete
	  CAD Objects dialogs when allocating the first vertice of a new CAD
	  Object.  It's a bit confusing when the windows move on top of the
	  drawing area when you do the first click, so I decided not to update
	  then.

