	  (1.83), src/draw_symbols.h (1.21): Adding a variable for doing
	  error_ellipses around posits.  Not in use yet.  Changed the position
	  ambiguity around so that it is correct and the symbol position
	  inside the rectangle is correct.  Still need to fix up the
	  grid-square code in the draw_ambiguity function though.

2006-06-15 21:28  we7u

	* src/draw_symbols.c (1.82): Fixing up some of the ambiguity
	  rectangle stuff.  All but the grid squares look ok now, but the
	  smallest rectangle ends up with the symbol placed off-center, which
	  still needs to be fixed.

