	  Canada topo file.  Thanks!

2006-05-31 20:39  we7u

	* src/igate.c (1.53): Disallowing igating of general queries in
	  either direction.  Directed queries still get gated as appropriate.

2006-05-31 20:36  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.539): Added some comments.

2006-05-31 19:57  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.538), src/wx.c (1.62): Fixing the backwards
	  conversions for wind speed for Peet Bros.  Ultimeter-II weather
	  stations.  The correct units are km/h if the sentence begins with
	  '#', and mph if the sentence begins with '*'.

2006-05-31 19:30  we7u

	* src/wx.c (1.61): Changes to comments/added some comments.

2006-05-31 18:39  we7u

	* src/wx.c (1.60): Zeroing the first two digits on wind speed for
	  Peet Bros 2k as per the docs.

2006-05-31 18:25  we7u

	* src/wx.c (1.59): Changing a few variables to make the code more
	  consistent.  Instead of pointing back to the original data to check
	  for ">7", we look at the first character of our substring
	  temp_data1[0].

2006-05-31 18:09  we7u

	* src/wx.c (1.58): Fixes for Peet weather stations, negative value
	  decoding.

2006-05-30 20:06  we7u

	* src/map_gnis.c (1.30): Fixes to make Xastir handle the type of
	  GNIS files found at:
	  <http://geonames.usgs.gov/domestic/download_data.htm> which have
	  shorter lines than the ones at: <http://geonames.usgs.gov/stategaz/>

2006-05-30 18:50  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.249): Really complicated fix for Xastir
	  dropping the last character of a packet.  A fix for the last fix I
	  put in.

2006-05-30 16:07  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.537): Changed one comment.

2006-05-30 15:18  we7u

	* src/database.h (1.27), src/db.c (1.536), src/interface.c (1.248),
	  src/main.c (1.697): A bug fix for KISS or AGWPE ports.  The AX.25
	  header increases in size when it gets converted to TAPR2-style
	  headers.  If there were enough digipeaters in the path then the
	  complete packet can get truncated on the tail-end.  This patch fixes
	  it by allocating a separate buffer that is quite large for each
	  packet before the header decoding function.

2006-05-17 19:28  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.535): Fixing the reply-ack problem during messaging.
	  It was an off-by-one error.  Our ack_string looked like "}5o"
	  instead of "5o", which made the comparison fail.

2006-05-13 16:27  we7u

	* src/Makefile.am (1.37): Adding rpl_malloc.h to the build.

2006-05-12 20:32  tvrusso

	* FAQ (1.65): Add command for converting Root files to new scheme.

	  Of course, if someone could check this file out to see the commands,
	  they've already done the conversion...

