	* README.win32 (1.133): Added a note about what to call COM1/COM2
	  in Cygwin.

2006-04-29 17:19  tvrusso

	* symbols/symbols.dat (1.27): Change \V symbol (VORTAC) to
	  something that looks like what the other APRS codes use, matching
	  the VORTAC symbol on aviation charts.

2006-04-24 19:21  we7u

	* src/alert.c (1.100), src/awk.c (1.34), src/bulletin_gui.c (1.37),
	  src/color.c (1.16), src/datum.c (1.23), src/db.c (1.534),
	  src/dbfawk.c (1.31), src/draw_symbols.c (1.79), src/fcc_data.c
	  (1.18), src/festival.c (1.20), src/geo-find.c (1.12),
	  src/geocoder_gui.c (1.21), src/gps.c (1.52), src/hashtable.c
	  (1.7), src/hashtable_itr.c (1.9), src/hostname.c (1.26),
	  src/igate.c (1.52), src/interface.c (1.247), src/interface_gui.c
	  (1.98), src/io-common.c (1.6), src/io-mmap.c (1.7), src/lang.c
