2006-02-19 19:48  tvrusso

	* scripts/Makefile.am (1.20), scripts/object2shp.pl (1.1): Per
	  discussion on xastir mailing list, a script to create shapefile maps
	  from the object.log file.  This will enable quick and dirty
	  generation of special purpose map overlays by plunking down objects,
	  creating shapefiles, then deleting the objects.

