	  MGRS to labeled grid border.

2006-02-03 17:46  chicoreus

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.207), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.196), config/language-French.sys (1.197),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.203), config/language-Italian.sys
