2005-10-20 01:29  we7u

	* src/map_WMS.c (1.18), src/map_geo.c (1.62), src/map_tif.c (1.33),
	  src/map_tiger.c (1.46): Commenting out the XFreeColors() calls
	  for now.  Cygwin seems to be much more sensitive to these calls than
	  Linux.

2005-10-19 20:24  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.236): Disabling sending of my own posits to
	  x_spider if transmit_disable is non-zero.

