	* src/objects.c (1.12): Added some comments.

2005-10-19 19:54  we7u

	* src/objects.c (1.11): Getting rid of "Transmitting objects/items"
	  statusline message if transmit of those types of packets is disabled
	  globally.

2005-10-19 19:21  we7u

	* src/map_WMS.c (1.17), src/map_geo.c (1.61), src/map_tif.c (1.32),
	  src/map_tiger.c (1.45): Adding XFreeColors() calls just before
	  each XAllocColor() call.  This is to keep the counters in sync that
	  count how many times each color is allocated, hopefully preventing
	  the can't allocate color warning messages.

