	  which fixes the gdal/geotiff bug.  This fix cuases the original
	  functions to be called if gdal isn't installed.

2005-10-14 18:06  we7u

	* src/map_tif.c (1.29): Received permission from Frank Warmerdam to
	  use some of his code inside Xastir, relicensing it under GPL.  We
	  use this new right to include one function in map_tif.c which allows
	  us to keep topo maps support even when libgdal is compiled in.

