2005-10-02 06:26  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.491), src/draw_symbols.c (1.77), src/geocoder_gui.c
	  (1.19), src/interface_gui.c (1.93), src/list_gui.c (1.38),
	  src/locate_gui.c (1.21), src/maps.c (1.449), src/xastir.h (1.47),
	  src/bulletin_gui.c (1.34), src/main.c (1.634), src/messages_gui.c
	  (1.46), src/objects.c (1.3), src/popup_gui.c (1.21),
	  src/track_gui.c (1.48), src/view_message_gui.c (1.31),
	  src/wx_gui.c (1.42): Getting rid of the Global.top widget which
	  was unmapped.  Making appshell be the top level widget.  Added
	  parsing for the -geometry command-line variable via XParseGeometry()
	  so that we can tell when either the height/width or the x/y offsets
	  have been specified.  We then set up appshell based on that info or
	  using the config file data if it wasn't specified on the
	  command-line.

