	* src/main.c (1.620): More mods for UDP->RF.  This version may be
	  working but it needs testing on a system with real RF interfaces to
	  see if it behaves properly.

2005-09-28 16:24  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.619), src/x_spider.c (1.45), src/x_spider.h (1.10):
	  Continuing work on support for UDP server port.  We're getting
	  closer now to supporting sending of packets to RF.

