2005-08-18 15:26  we7u

	* src/leak_detection.h (1.2): Here's where the malloc and dmalloc
	  code was moved to.  The order in which this is done with respect to
	  the libgc code is critical, therefore it has all been moved to this
	  one header file so the order can be closely guarded.

