2005-08-17 19:04  we7u

	* src/Makefile.am (1.29): Adding the leak_detector.h file.

2005-08-17 19:02  we7u

	* src/leak_detection.h (1.1): Moving the LIBGC defines/includes
	  into a new header file.  The order in which these are used in a C
	  module is important, as is the order that the thread includes are
	  done.  This will help assure that the order remains consistent so
	  that the memory leak detection will work.

