2005-08-03 19:01  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.470): Added emergency beacon decode for the string
	  "EMERGENCY" anywhere in the packet, plus the strings:
	      ALARM
	      ALERT
	      WARNING
	      WXALARM
	      EM If seen in the TO: field of the packet.  This matches the
	  decoding provided by APRS+SA for this feature.

