	* WMSRadar.geo (1.7): Changing a comment.

2005-06-14 21:01  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.224): Commenting out a debug fprintf
	  statement.

2005-06-14 19:59  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.223), src/interface.h (1.32): Adding a #define
	  in interface.h called CONVERSE_MODE.  This can be set to "k" or
	  "conv" via different defines to account for different TNC command
	  sets.

2005-06-14 19:39  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.222): Changed some comments.

2005-06-14 02:45  we7u

	* config/Makefile.am (1.22), config/tnc-startup.tnc2 (1.1): Adding
	  a TAPR-2 style startup file.  This one is mostly a copy of the
	  tnc-startup.paccomm file for the moment, but will probably diverge
	  from it over time.

2005-06-10 16:55  tvrusso

	* src/db.c (1.463): Add additional check on wx stations to aloha
	  calculations.  APRSDos only checks the symbol for "_", we were only
	  checking if there's any WX data.  I was finding that some stations
	  with _ symbols were not being classed as wx stations, apparently
	  because their last posit had no weather or something.

	  Add "_" to the test.

2005-06-10 01:19  we7u

	* DEBUG_LEVELS (1.11): Adding Multipoint to the 2048 level
	  description.  Naming the function in main.c that must be changed if
	  more levels are added.

2005-06-09 05:08  tvrusso

	* DEBUG_LEVELS (1.10), config/language-Dutch.sys (1.169),
	  config/language-English.sys (1.158), config/language-French.sys
	  (1.160), config/language-German.sys (1.164),
	  config/language-Italian.sys (1.162),
	  config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.159),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.169), src/database.h (1.17),
	  src/db.c (1.462), src/main.c (1.573): Several improvements of
	  ALOHA reporting, as discussed on xastir-dev

	  1) Change #ifdef DEBUG_ALOHA to a debug level test (2048)
	  2) Add periodic display of ALOHA range in status line
	  3) Add a "View->ALOHA Statistics" menu option.  Pops up a dialog
	     with ALOHA range, number of stations in ALOHA circle, count of
	     various types of stations, and age of ALOHA calculation.

2005-06-08 16:00  we7u

	* FAQ (1.53): Adding a bit about how to turn off the aloha circle
	  display.

2005-06-08 15:45  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.572): Calculating the Aloha circle even if the
	  feature is turned off.  This means that if the feature is turned
	  back on again the circle will be accurate.  The processing occurs so
	  seldom anyway that it's not much of a hit.

2005-06-08 05:33  tvrusso

	* src/map_tiger.c (1.32): Fix initialization of local_filename[0]
	  so that gcc 2.95 can compile this file.

2005-06-08 05:16  tvrusso

	* src/db.c (1.461): Fix mistake in logic of aloha_distance() that
	  was letting some oddly configured mobiles to slip through the cracks
	  (those with trackpoints and no speed).

2005-06-07 20:04  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.168), config/language-English.sys
