	  the aloha toggle code.  Changing the name of the toggle and callback
	  to be more consistent with the rest of the code.

2005-06-07 19:54  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.167), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.156), config/language-French.sys (1.158),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.162), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.160), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.157),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.167), src/db.c (1.459), src/main.c
	  (1.570), src/main.h (1.78): Adding an option to disable the Aloha
	  Circle.  This option is not saved to the config file, by choice.
	  It's intended that the Aloha circle be on the map for the default
	  case so that people might make use of it.  The toggle has been added
	  for those rare cases where the Aloha Circle needs to be removed from
	  the screen.

