	  compilation warnings.

2005-06-07 06:06  tvrusso

	* src/database.h (1.16): Put an ifdef around a struct element only
	  used for debugging.  This should cut down on memory use during ALOHA
	  calculation when not debugging.

2005-06-07 05:54  tvrusso

	* FAQ (1.52), src/database.h (1.15), src/db.c (1.458),
