2005-04-15 17:02  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.218), src/interface.h (1.31),
	  src/interface_gui.c (1.88), src/xa_config.c (1.132): Changes by
	  Andreas Bier, DL1HRC, to allow setting a tnc2multi into KISS mode
	  via a togglebutton on the interface dialog.  We can probably extend
	  this later to put other types of TNC's into KISS mode and/or to take
	  them out of KISS mode when shutting down the interface.

	  I also changed the default for new interfaces to have RELAY/WIDE1-1
	  digipeat turned off.

