	  discussions to cover the new scheme (WIDE1-1 instead of RELAY).

2005-04-06 19:26  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.454), src/util.c (1.159): Making the "RELAY" digipeat
	  work with either RELAY or WIDE1-1, per the latest APRSSIG
	  recommendations on how to do paths and digipeating.

