	* scripts/fcc-get (1.9), src/fcc_data.c (1.13), src/main.c (1.558),
	  src/rac_data.c (1.12), src/xa_config.c (1.130): Minor tweaks to
	  fcc-get script.  Dump text to stderr if we're re-indexing the fcc or
	  rac data.  Bumped max tiger timeout from 180 sec to 300 sec.

2005-02-04 18:34  we7u

