2005-01-08 10:06  we7u

	* src/alert.c (1.84), src/awk.c (1.25), src/bulletin_gui.c (1.29),
	  src/color.c (1.11), src/datum.c (1.20), src/dbfawk.c (1.26),
	  src/draw_symbols.c (1.61), src/fcc_data.c (1.12), src/festival.c
	  (1.15), src/geocoder_gui.c (1.14), src/gps.c (1.45),
	  src/hostname.c (1.17), src/igate.c (1.42), src/interface.c
	  (1.210), src/interface_gui.c (1.85), src/lang.c (1.12),
