	  Displaying the message timer interval in the Send Message dialog for
	  active messages.

2004-11-30 20:24  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.155), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.145), config/language-French.sys (1.147),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.151), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.149), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.146),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.156), src/messages.c (1.41),
	  src/messages.h (1.10), src/messages_gui.c (1.30): Updates to
	  messenging.  We can now see queued messages before they get to the
	  transmit stage.  New button added to kick the timer back to original
	  values (to get a QSO going again).  Timer value is currently sent to
	  STDERR, but will eventually be placed into the Send Message GUI as
	  well.

