	* src/map_gdal.c (1.106): Starting to support proper color scheme
	  for SDTS-format maps.  At least have contours in yellow and other
	  layers in black now.

2004-10-19 04:08  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.105): Fixing OGR indexing so that the transform
	  is invoked every time.  Required for UTM/State-plane maps.

2004-10-18 20:17  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.420): Changing default Shapefile translator back to
	  Shapelib.

2004-10-18 20:09  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.104): Truncating the points better.  Was
	  truncating at 0 for negative values, which doesn't work.  We just
	  need to keep away from the +16000/-16000 points and greater, which
	  invoke X11 drawing bugs.  Truncating at zero creates dummy lines
	  along our top and left window borders.

2004-10-18 19:58  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.103): Very weak attempt at detecting
	  hypsography and hydropraphy SDTS files to decide to color them
	  yellow, keyed off "HY"or "HP" anywhere in the full filename (that's
	  why it is weak).  Other SDTS maps get colored black currently.

