	* src/map_gdal.c (1.92): Several fixes.  Spatial filtering now
	  works properly.

2004-10-14 19:52  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.91): Simplified some of the code.  Have SDTS
	  contours working again, but have a problem with those files and
	  spatial filtering yet.  This version works but puts out error
	  messages to STDERR with SDTS files.

2004-10-14 06:05  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.90): Sped up GDAL maps:  Implemented the
	  spatial filtering mechanism inherent in the library.  We now filter
	  using our viewport as the bounding rectangle, which really speeds
	  things up as you zoom in.

2004-10-14 05:57  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.418): Fix for draw_vector function.  It now
	  rearranges the bottom/top/left/right if it's called with things out
	  of order, before calling map_visible.  This gets fewer vectors
	  rejected due to being off-screen/more vectors actually get drawn.

