	  (not complete yet).

2004-10-06 05:17  shadow

	* src/awk.c (1.24): awk_find_sym can return NULL; don't assume
	  src->type is valid.

2004-10-06 00:20  shadow

	* config/tgr2shp.dbfawk (1.2): dd missing double-quote in FENAME
	  default case handling

2004-10-05 17:11  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.392), src/main.c (1.529): Fixing the Move Object
	  function so that we can only move objects that we already own.  Any
	  SSID will work.  If we don't own it, we have to adopt the object
	  first before we can move it.  This keeps us from accidentally moving
	  objects if we accidentally leave the Move function on and then
	  click/drag on the map display.

2004-10-05 15:54  we7u

	* Makefile.am (1.29): Adding a new Texas radar geo file.

