2004-09-03 15:16  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.381): Drawing symbol after we draw circles and other
	  items.  Trying to keep the text on top so that it is more readable.

2004-09-03 05:37  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.380): Moving the weather info to the top of the
	  Station Info dialog, for the cases where we have weather info
	  stored.  The weather info is the most important info for that
	  station in that case, so it should be readable without scrolling.
	  Stations without weather data are unaffected by this change.

2004-09-03 03:19  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.379): Fixed a small bug in positionless weather
	  decoding where it wasn't decoding course/speed fields.  We now take
	  another look for course/speed if either of them are empty.  Before
	  both of them had to be empty before we tried another type of parsing
	  for them.  Did the and->or conversion in several places in
	  extract_weather(), so the change affects more than just positionless
	  weather packets.

