2004-08-20 16:52  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.144), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.138), config/language-French.sys (1.139),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.143), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.141), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.138),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.148): Reducing the resolution on
	  the snow reports, as they are only reported by inch, not by 100's of
	  an inch.

