	  drag/drop objects/items that are right on top of each other.  The
	  selection dialog will pop up so you can choose which one to move.

2004-08-14 16:43  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.507): Fixing object/item generation so that a space
	  is prefixed to the comment field only in the case where multipoint
	  polygons are present.  The space is necessary in order to parse
	  multipoint objects properly, but is not desired for other
	  objects/items where it would limit the extent of the comment.

