	* src/db.c (1.338): Fixing a bug Reuven found:  Doing an "if" based
	  on the value of an uninitialized variable.

2004-06-30 20:53  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.337): Fixing an indexing bug that Reuven found (via
	  "valgrind").  We can't go past index 0 if we've assigned '\0' to a
	  string.

2004-06-30 20:36  rzg

	* src/color.c (1.9), src/dbfawk.c (1.22), src/main.c (1.480): Minor
	  memory leak fixes.

