	* src/list_gui.c (1.28): Fixing a memory leak that Reuven
	  discovered.

2004-06-30 19:43  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.336): Fixing a bug found by Reuven in the GLL decode
	  routine.

2004-06-30 17:54  we7u

	* src/db.h (1.52), src/db.c (1.335): Moved multipoints into a
	  separate record, allocating only when needed.  This provides
	  additional memory savings over the tweaks that went in yesterday,
	  with no loss in speed/efficiency.

2004-06-30 03:45  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.334), src/db.h (1.51): Tweaks to significantly reduce
	  memory usage.

2004-06-29 19:42  we7u

	* src/wx.c (1.38): Fixing all the 2^16 constants.  Ten of them were
	  incorrect.

