	* src/db.c (1.331), src/main.c (1.474): Removing tac-call
	  capability for objects/items.  The saving/restoring of these on
	  startup is a problem.  Perhaps we can add the functionality back in
	  later for these, but probably only if we own the objects/items
	  ourselves.  Even then, deleting the objects/items needs to be looked
	  at carefully.

