	* src/util.c (1.102): Changing one debug fprintf.

2004-06-14 20:40  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.163): Removing an error messaging having to do
	  with the tnc-start/stop META tag.  This error message gets thrown
	  out at odd times if you happen to have META in a comment in those
	  file.  Not needed.

