	  protocols don't show up in converse/monitor mode.

2004-06-04 05:49  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.462): Zoom-in box tweaks.  These prevent the
	  vectors from being drawn over again if a screen update has happened.
	  Keeps extra line segments from appearing while doing the zoom-in box
	  mouse operation.

