2004-05-28 19:23  we7u

	* config/nwsc_ddmmyy.dbfawk (1.10), config/nwsfz_ddmmyy.dbfawk
	  (1.3), config/nwsmzddmmyy.dbfawk (1.7), config/nwsozddmmyy.dbfawk
