	* src/db.c (1.319): Had to move the variable declarations up in the
	  code block, else it fails compile on FreeBSD.  Thanks to Tom Russo
	  for this fix.

2004-05-17 20:06  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.318): A small tweak to make the FCC/RAC lookup for
	  objects/items look at the FROM callsign instead of the object/item
	  names.  Now we can look up who is sending the objects in our
	  database.

2004-05-17 19:44  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.317): Fixing the weather alert by "Station Info"
	  lookups so that it works for more objects from the weather server.

2004-05-17 18:45  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.128), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.124), config/language-French.sys (1.124),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.128), config/language-Italian.sys
