2004-03-08 21:13  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.123), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.119), config/language-French.sys (1.119),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.123), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.121), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.119),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.129), src/db.c (1.303),
	  src/igate.c (1.27), src/interface.c (1.157), src/interface.h
	  (1.27), src/interface_gui.c (1.65), src/main.c (1.447): Initial
	  stab at creating a new SERIAL_MKISS interface type.  So far it's an
	  identical copy of the SERIAL_KISS interface type, but that will
	  change soon.  Intent is to support multi-port KISS TNC's such as the
	  Kantronics KAM.

