2004-02-12 22:18  we7u

	* src/interface.h (1.26), src/interface.c (1.155): New method of
	  waiting for data to get to serial TNC's before closing the port.
	  Method and most of the code contributed by Erik G. Burrows, KG6HEA.
	  Additional code by WE7U to prevent locking up with poorly-behaved
	  serial devices.

2004-02-11 22:40  we7u

	* src/map_geo.c (1.23): Making transparent images work again after
	  the raster_intensity changes a few weeks back.

2004-02-11 21:35  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.443): Fixing an annoying floating-point conversion
	  bug in the Map Intensity menus.  For 70% and 90%, they were reported
	  as 60% and 80% in the menus.

