	* src/xa_config.c (1.107): Attempting to recover from backup file
	  renaming when things go wrong.  We'll try to get as close to the
	  original state of the files as we can.

2004-01-15 21:09  we7u

	* src/xa_config.c (1.106): More config file backup copies code.  We
	  now back out the renaming if the new config file can't be created,
	  so we're left with the original config and two backups in that case.

2004-01-15 19:02  we7u

	* FAQ (1.23), src/interface.c (1.153), src/interface_gui.c (1.61),
	  src/xa_config.c (1.105): Simplified the all interfaces up/down
	  logic.  It should work better now.  Changed the config file backup
	  code so that xastir.cnf.1 through xastir.cnf.3 are created.  This
	  should help insulate us a bit better from crashes, as we'll have
	  more old copies of the config file to draw from if the main config
	  file (xastir.cnf) gets trashed.

2004-01-15 16:56  we7u

	* configure.ac (1.75): Adding a line in for getting rid of
	  duplicates in the LIBS variable.  Commented out while testing so
	  that it doesn't hurt any installations.

