2003-12-08 23:43  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.147): Checking that I can stat a file and that
	  it is a regular file before attempting to send a file of commands to
	  the TNC.

2003-12-08 21:22  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.39): Adding indexing for files where spatial
	  coordinate system is not known, but they still fall within the
	  normal lat/long boundaries for file extents.  We're assuming they're
	  in geographic WGS84 coordinates in this case and allowing the
	  indexing to complete.

2003-12-08 20:56  jtwilley

	* config/tnc-startup.null (1.1): Added a zero-byte file named
	  'tnc-startup.null' for those times when users do not want their TNC
	  configurations changed by xastir.

2003-12-08 20:19  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.38): Comment updates.  No code changes this
	  time.

2003-12-08 20:10  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.37): Took out some debug stuff that messed with
	  converting to nad27 datum for test runs.  Generalized the code so
	  that it works with projected coordinate systems.  No computes file
	  extents for state-plane coordinate systems.  It should also work for
	  UTM projected coordinate systems.

2003-12-08 07:50  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.36): For file extents (indexing):  Datum
	  translation is working now for geographic coordinate systems.  Not
	  implemented yet for projected coordinate systems.  Haven't
	  implemented datum translation for drawing yet.

2003-12-08 07:47  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.389): Forcing shapefiles back to the old code for
	  now.

2003-12-08 07:46  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.388): More debug for map_driver stuff.

2003-12-07 20:23  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.146): Reducing delay in port_write for
	  checking queue.  Down to 100us from 200ms.  Makes writing to
	  interfaces much snappier, but doesn't bog down CPU.  Cranking up
	  channel_data() busy wait from 1 to 2us.

2003-12-07 17:16  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.428), src/xa_config.c (1.104): Fixing the 10% zoom
	  in bug when at zoom level 1.

2003-12-06 20:10  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.35): Filling in a bit more for the OGR indexing
	  code.

2003-12-06 17:20  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.145): Reducing many of the usleep() delays
	  while transmitting to serial TNC's.  Users will have to rely on the
	  new delay slider to add delays if they get into weird operation with
	  any particular TNC.

2003-12-06 07:44  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.34): More changes to debug output.

2003-12-06 07:36  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.33): Partial map indexing working for OGR.
	  Must be geographic coordinate system.  Haven't implemented
	  conversions from other datums or coordinate systems to geographic
	  WGS84/NAD83 yet.

