	* src/map_gdal.c (1.24): Changed some comments.

2003-12-04 18:08  we7u

	* src/map_gdal.c (1.23): Adding map interrupt capability to the OGR
	  code.

2003-12-04 16:39  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.387): Fixing up the callouts to GDAL/OGR.  We
	  direct Shapefile stuff to draw_shapefile_map() right now instead of
	  GDAL/OGR.  Tiger goes to GDAL/OGR.  This can be changed via a define
	  near the top of maps.c so that Shapefile goes to OGR as well.

