2003-10-29 21:03  we7u

	* src/datum.c (1.10), src/datum.h (1.7), src/maps.c (1.369): Fixing
	  the UTM grid.  Added "MGRS_grid" variable.  If set, we draw the
	  irregular grids and report UTM coordinates using those grids.  If
	  zero, we draw the regularly-spaced six-degree zones and report using
	  those regular zones.

