2003-10-18 03:22  we7u

	* src/datum.c (1.6): Temporarily making the easting and northing
	  for the UPS areas (near the poles) equal to all zeroes.  This is to
	  prevent someone thinking that the numbers we're showing are valid
	  coordinates.  We haven't been computing proper coordinates in the
	  UPS areas.  Am still working on the problem and hope to have valid
	  UPS numbers by the end of the weekend.

