2003-10-13 04:22  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.351), src/maps.c (1.338), src/xastir.h (1.30):
	  Attempting to fix the snapshot problem where stations disappear off
	  the display.  Created another Pixmap:  pixmap_snapshot, and copy
	  pixmap_final to it just before the snapshot thread is started.  This
	  should separate any accesses to the data so that no conflicts occur
	  while making the snapshot.

