2003-10-09 19:47  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.331): Changing the smaller UTM grids to display in
	  bright yellow.  Easier to see on maps.

2003-10-09 16:18  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.330): Initial attempt at finer UTM grids, using
	  preliminary code by Olivier Calle
	  (N7TAP).  The code handles the irregular regions near/above Norway
	  for the major UTM grid zones only (not for the minor grids yet).
	  There are known problems near the zone boundaries with lines not
	  getting drawn or incorrect lines getting drawn.  For the most part,
	  if you're inside a zone and not in the irregular zone area, this
	  code works very well, and is very fast!

2003-10-09 16:03  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.285), src/main.c (1.350), src/map_geo.c (1.11):
	  Changing a few printf's to fprintf's.

