	* src/maps.c (1.277): On-line topo maps.  I considered the utility
	  of this versus not adding it until after release.  This is just too
	  useful for new (and old) users not to have put it in.  Enjoy!  Geo
	  file with "TOPOSERVER" in it will get you online topo maps.

