	  option for AGWPE interfaces.  This can be adapted to other
	  multi-port TNC interfaces later.

2003-04-11 20:26  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.101): Backing out one change to avoid high
	  CPU-usage in the port_write() function.  Added comments to the
	  port_read() and port_write() threads to hopefully eliminate this
	  sort of problem in the future.

2003-04-11 18:17  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.100): Added code to disable Nagle's algorithm
	  for TCP/IP sockets : TCP_NODELAY setsockopt().

2003-04-11 17:25  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.99): Eliminated line pacing for network
	  connections.  Added more serial types to the character pacing code.

2003-04-11 00:10  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.98): Fixing a lock problem and commenting out
	  some debug packets for AGWPE.

