	* src/interface.c (1.88): More AGWPE stuff.  Not functional yet.

2003-04-04 20:52  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.87): Send the login packet to AGWPE only if
	  the passwd string has something in it.

2003-04-04 19:48  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.86): More AGWPE interface code.  Now sending
	  login/password string and command to ask AGWPE to send us the
	  monitored packets.  Don't have transmit or the receive decode of
	  those packets completed yet, but debug code is in place that looks
	  for complete headers and packets and notifies us on reception.

