	  installation of libgeotiff.

2003-02-27 20:53  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.236): Preliminary support for GPSMan:  Downloads
	  track, creates Shapefile map, auto-imports and displays said map in
	  Xastir.  Requires pre-release GPSMan plus gpsmanshp.tgz file
	  installed.  Also requires that the "WE7U" define at the top of
	  main.c be defined to put the new code into operation.

