2003-02-24 23:26  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.213), src/maps.c (1.220), src/maps.h (1.19): Starting
	  to change the weather alert code to make it independent of the
	  message database.  Part-way to that goal.  This version just
	  relocates the weather alerts scan of the message database into the
	  db.c code at the point where we received the alert.  The next step
	  is to just throw the alert onto the alert_list and skip the message
	  database portion altogether.  This current code appears to still be
	  fully functional w.r.t. weather alerts.

