2003-02-20 23:31  we7u

	* src/bulletin_gui.c (1.14): A few fixes for bulletins.  Also added
	  a callback for the togglebutton on the View->Bulletins dialog.

2003-02-20 22:34  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.212): Added a debugging message.

2003-02-20 22:18  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.228): Changing the "Test" function a bit.

2003-02-20 20:00  we7u

	* src/bulletin_gui.c (1.13): Changing time between receiving a new
	  bulletin and checking whether it is within our range:  From 15
	  seconds to 60 seconds.  This actually delays our getting notice of
	  each new bulletin, but helps to prevent popping up bulletins when a
	  bulletin comes in and then a posit comes in later for that station
	  (putting that station outside our range).  The cause of the bulletin
	  window popping up appears to be these inside-our-range/
	  outside-our-range-when-a-posit-comes-in bulletins.

2003-02-20 19:32  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.210): Changed/added some comments.  No code
	  changes.

