	* src/main.c (1.215): Changing max posit rate to every 60 minutes
	  instead of every 45.

2003-02-03 20:56  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.214): Added separate object/item TX timer and
	  associated slider in Configure->Defaults.  Now people with WX
	  stations that want to transmit every 5 minutes can set their
	  object/item TX rate separately.  Also changed the posit rate slider
	  to go from 0.5 to 45 minutes (30 seconds to 45 minutes).

