	* src/festival.h (1.2), src/festival.c (1.7): Fixed the non-connect
	  to Festival Server problem.  This problem existed when Festival was
	  started up after Xastir.  Now Xastir will try to connect to the
	  server when speech is desired, but will not try a new socket
	  connection any more often than every 60 seconds.

2003-01-14 17:19  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.195): Print a warning in draw_geo_image_map() if
	  the image file cannot be read for some reason (typically permissions
	  problems).

2003-01-14 06:23  kd6zwr

	* src/main.c (1.198): Added error checking for setting my station
	  postion from mouse popup menu.

2003-01-14 05:33  kd6zwr

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.68), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.67), config/language-French.sys (1.67),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.67), config/language-Italian.sys
