2003-01-13 06:22  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.185), src/interface.c (1.56), src/interface.h (1.17),
	  src/main.c (1.196): Added some debugging statements in the
	  extract_weather functions.  Added a new global string that holds the
	  last packet processed by file read or channel_data functions.  If a
	  segfault occurs, this last packet is dumped to STDERR along with the
	  segfault message.  This might help in the future to find "killer"
	  packets.

