2002-12-20 20:36  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.169): Added some comments.

2002-12-20 20:07  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.186): Changing the manual map index button back to
	  its original code, where it only updates the map index instead of
	  re-indexing from scratch.  This keeps the manually-tweaked map_level
	  & draw_filled fields intact.  The original reason for starting from
	  scratch was to remove deleted maps.  This happens anyway after two
	  Xastir restarts, so starting the list from scratch isn't really
	  needed anyway.

