	  user can specify which maps go on which layer, and which layers to
	  enable for drawing.

2002-12-19 20:36  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.65), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.64), config/language-French.sys (1.64),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.64), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.65), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.62),
