	  count of how many maps are currently selected to the map chooser.
	  Doesn't quite work the way I'd like yet, but it is useful.  It shows
	  how many maps are marked in the in-memory map index as selected.
	  That quantity can change when you tweak things in the map chooser
	  and then hit OK.

2002-12-19 06:03  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.64), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.63), config/language-French.sys (1.63),
