	  occur at roughly the same time.

2002-11-22 00:50  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.56), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.55), config/language-French.sys (1.55),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.55), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.56), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.52),
