	  ON.

2002-11-19 00:25  francais1

	* src/draw_symbols.c (1.23), src/main.c (1.165): Added call to
	  draw_symbols in UpdateTime at least every 30 s if dead reckoning
	  drawing is turned on.  Tweaked dead reckoning graphics to draw the
	  DR trail in a dashed line and draw an arc that gets larger as time
	  from last posit grows until it turns into a circle.

2002-11-18 21:19  we7u

	* src/draw_symbols.c (1.22): Fixing the bug where weather stations
	  hit the clear interval but wind barbs still get drawn.

2002-11-18 05:48  kd6zwr

	* src/main.c (1.164): added keysyms for pgup/pgdn on sun keyboards

2002-11-15 02:02  we7u

	* src/util.c (1.40): Code to handle disowning of object that other
	  people take over, and to comment out our own objects from the
	  object.log file when we delete them.  This keeps us from
	  retransmitting the objects when Xastir restarts.

2002-11-15 00:25  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.163), src/util.c (1.39), src/util.h (1.12): More
	  object stuff.  More to do yet.

2002-11-14 23:50  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.174), src/util.c (1.38), src/util.h (1.11): The start
	  of code to allow disowning an object that someone else is assuming
	  control over.  Xastir already does this while running, but it
	  doesn't write the data to the object.log file, so when it starts up,
	  it owns the object again.

2002-11-14 22:07  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.173): Saving empty-string for speed instead of "0" if
	  speed is unknown on a parsed packet.

2002-11-14 20:40  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.172): Unlinking DR functions from Display
	  Course/Speed toggles.

2002-11-14 19:30  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.54), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.53), config/language-French.sys (1.53),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.53), config/language-Italian.sys
