	  index.  Lot's of tweaks to sort the map index.  Now use the .geo
	  filenames instead of the http/ftp URL's.  Got rid of shx/dbf
	  filenames (using shp instead).  This got rid of the triple-drawing
	  of shapefiles that was ocurring with automaps.  Added statusline()
	  calls to all of the draw functions.

