	  WAY too long when I defined 30 interfaces.  The new length is more
	  reasonable.

2002-09-30 23:06  we7u

	* src/interface.h (1.16), src/interface_gui.c (1.30), src/main.c
	  (1.143): Upp'ed the number of interface to 15.  Tweaked the GUI
	  and other portions of the code to handle whatever MAX_IFACE_DEVICES
	  is set to.  Xastir should theoretically be able to handle any number
	  of interfaces now, but it's only been tested so far up to 15.

