	  of grid square location lowercase since that seems more common.

2002-08-14 15:49  francais1

	* src/main.c (1.127): Nasty lat/lon to/from UTM conversion bug.
	  (Wasn't referencing correct ellipsoid.)

2002-08-14 00:12  we7u

	* scripts/permutations.pl (1.1): New script which will show various
	  permutations for a lat/lon or UTM input.  Eventually plan to have
	  this script write a log file containing objects so that Xastir can
	  plot each of the positions.  This will be useful in quickly
	  determining which of the formats is within the area of interest.
	  Developed this for Search & Rescue applications.

