2002-08-06 20:00  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.125), src/util.c (1.29), src/util.h (1.8),
	  src/xastir.h (1.14): Implementation of persistent objects/items.
	  Each new, deleted, or moved object/item is logged to
	  "~/.xastir/config/object.log".  This file is read in and each line
	  processed on startup.  This will also show tracklines for moved
	  objects as each change is logged to the file.

