2002-08-05 20:48  we7u

	* src/bulletin_gui.c (1.5), src/draw_symbols.c (1.13),
	  src/location_gui.c (1.2), src/main.c (1.124), src/messages_gui.c
	  (1.13), src/track_gui.c (1.5), src/view_message_gui.c (1.6),
	  src/xastir.h (1.13): Added defines for foreground and background
	  font colors.  This and the associated code changes should help to
	  alleviate the problem where font colors would accidentally change
	  during runtime due to color-ls being run in the starting Xterm.

