	  1.1.3.  Getting ready for another development release.

2002-07-22 17:41  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.122), src/interface_gui.c (1.26): Commenting out
	  debug message.  Making Relay Digipeat togglebuttons insensitive
	  until the code to implement them is functional.

2002-07-20 07:44  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.121): Don't relay from KISS interface if transmit for
	  that interface is turned off.

2002-07-20 07:31  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.25): Changes to make RELAY digipeat
	  insensitive when transmit is disabled for that interface.

2002-07-20 06:50  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.46): Commenting out another debug statement.

2002-07-20 06:48  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.45): Fixes to AX.25 interfaces that were
	  broken earlier by KISS TNC changes.

2002-07-20 00:02  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.44): Changes to serial lockfiles.  Now closes
	  port before removing lock.  Attempts to close port and remove lock
	  if open fails for any number of reasons.

2002-07-19 22:19  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.43): Fixes for errant long packets.  Code had
	  the wrong number for the length of the incoming strings.

2002-07-19 20:51  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.120), src/interface.c (1.42): Found an off-by-one
	  error in incoming_data_length.  Changed a lot of comments w.r.t.
	  KISS interfaces.

2002-07-19 08:06  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.119), src/db.h (1.17), src/interface.c (1.41),
