	* help/help-English.dat (1.22): Changed KISS interface description
	  to agree with the code, which forces the N81 option for serial port
	  parameters now.

2002-07-18 19:37  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.20): Forcing KISS interfaces to N81 for
	  the serial port parameters.

2002-07-18 19:17  we7u

	* help/help-English.dat (1.21): Just spelling fixes.

2002-07-18 19:14  we7u

