2002-07-12 23:59  we7u

	* src/messages_gui.c (1.7): Adding some code in preparation for
	  setting up individual return paths for messaging.  This code figures
	  out the return path from the last path received for that station,
	  including dropping "RELAY" callsigns and asterisks and converting
	  WIDEn-N callsigns to their original glory.  Converts TRACE and
	  TRACEn-N callsigns to WIDE and WIDEn-N as well.

2002-07-12 21:09  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.32), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.32), config/language-French.sys (1.32),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.32), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.33), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.27),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.34), src/db.c (1.109), src/igate.c
	  (1.6), src/interface.c (1.24), src/interface.h (1.7),
	  src/interface_gui.c (1.14), src/main.c (1.113), src/messages.c
	  (1.19), src/wx.c (1.16), src/xa_config.c (1.38): Implemented
	  separate unproto path for igating.  Change it via the properties
	  dialog for affected interfaces.  If nothing entered, it will
	  round-robin between the other three interfaces or select a default
	  path.

