2002-06-25 22:03  we7u

	* src/bulletin_gui.c (1.3), src/bulletin_gui.h (1.2), src/db.c
	  (1.83): Fixes for annoying bulletins.  It should only pop up the
	  bulletin dialog now when new bulletins come in that are within
	  range.  It's possible to receive a bulletin without having a posit
	  from that station, then get a posit, making it outside the range.
	  In this case you may get a popup without knowing why.  It's better
	  than what it was doing before though.

