	* src/db.c (1.70), src/main.c (1.92): Commenting out debug
	  printf's.  Changed some other comments.

2002-06-17 21:40  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.69): More comments.  Another tweak to SmartBeaconing:
	  If we've sped up a bit the code will now bring the next beacon in
	  closer (in time), instead of waiting for the next slow beacon to
	  reset to the slower interval.

2002-06-17 21:16  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.68): Added a few SmartBeaconing comments.

2002-06-17 20:11  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.67), src/main.c (1.91): Another few SmartBeaconing
	  tweaks.  Setting defaults for variables to prevent multiple beacons
	  as we get started.

2002-06-17 19:19  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.66), src/main.c (1.90): A few SmartBeaconing tweaks.
	  Commented out the experimental SmartBeaconing tweaks that caused a
	  beacon when entering/exiting stop mode.  Changed how other
	  SmartBeaconing math was done.

2002-06-17 18:42  we7u

	* src/draw_symbols.c (1.6): Added color-coding for
	  time-since-last-heard display.  Green for 0-29 mins, Yellow for
	  30-59 minutes, Red for 60 mins to infinity.  This is to help keep
	  track of which stations are active and which haven't been heard for
	  a while.

2002-06-17 17:16  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.65): Moved the "reversed symbol" message into a debug
	  level.

