	* README.1ST (1.15): Removed reference to putting TIGERMAP in a
	  .geo file which no longer works.

2002-06-01 00:32  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.42): Initial attempt to handle Reply/Ack messaging
	  protocol (on the receive side only).  Only implemented for APRS
	  messaging, not UI-View messaging.

2002-05-31 21:24  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.41): Fixes for last_ack timer.  We now refuse to send
	  ack's or auto_answer messages any faster than every 30 seconds, even
	  if multiple interfaces are sending us copies of the same message.

2002-05-31 19:36  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.93): Simplified the print properties dialog.
	  Commented out unused options.

2002-05-30 15:04  n0vh

	* src/igate.c (1.4): More cleanup of the status messages written to
	  the console.

2002-05-30 04:32  n0vh

	* src/igate.c (1.3): Cleaned up some of the status messages by
	  adding a newline to the end.

2002-05-30 00:07  francais1

	* src/maps.c (1.92): Imagemagick drawing speedup for some cases.

2002-05-29 23:59  francais1

	* src/util.c (1.19), src/util.h (1.6): Added a simple function to
	  roughly time code execution.

2002-05-28 16:48  we7u

	* src/xa_config.c (1.22): Patch for incorrect lat/long limits by
	  Henk de Groot, PE1DNN.  Thanks Henk!

2002-05-25 00:07  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.40), src/db.h (1.4): Attempting to get rid of
	  duplicate ack's and autoreply messages.  This attempt is at least
	  partially successful.

2002-05-24 22:01  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.39), src/util.c (1.18): Fixed spelling error in
	  util.c.  Fixes for incorrect sorting in Send Message window for the
	  case where the remote client has restarted and is re-using sequence
	  numbers: Xastir will now replace the older messages in the database
	  and update the timestamp, which keeps the proper ordering for a QSO.
	  Messages older than 8 hours with the same text will also get
	  replaced and get a new timestamp.

2002-05-22 21:05  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.10), src/interface.c (1.15), src/interface_gui.c
	  (1.13), src/xa_config.c (1.21): Mods for CYGWIN by Charles
	  Suprin, AA1VS.

2002-05-21 21:33  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.38): Getting rid of unneeded extra message_update()
	  calls.

2002-05-21 19:27  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.37): More messaging fixes.

2002-05-21 19:02  we7u

	* src/messages_gui.c (1.5), src/db.c (1.36): Fixes for text
	  corruption in Send Message window.  Needs further testing.

2002-05-21 17:19  we7u

	* src/util.c (1.17), src/view_message_gui.c (1.4): Fixing distance
	  calculation such that it returns 0.0 if we haven't heard a posit
	  from the remote station yet.

2002-05-21 16:18  we7u

	* src/view_message_gui.c (1.3): View->Messages history dump now
	  obeys the distance limit set at the top of the form.

2002-05-20 21:49  we7u

	* src/view_message_gui.c (1.2), src/xa_config.c (1.20): We now dump
	  all currently active messages out to the view->messages window when
	  it's first opened.  Different format, but still useful.  The format
	  is easily tweaked later.  Also changed the default
	  VIEW_MESSAGE_LIMIT to 10000.  This can be tweaked by the user in the
	  ~/.xastir/xastir.cnf file.  Max allowed by the code is now 99999.

2002-05-18 07:06  kd6zwr

	* src/maps.c (1.91): Draw symbols for GNIS files.

2002-05-17 23:55  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.14): Temporary fix for CYGWIN.  Disables use
	  of HSP adapter.  Better fix needs to be implemented.

2002-05-17 23:52  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.12): Mods for CYGWIN.

2002-05-17 22:56  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.74), src/messages_gui.c (1.4): Added <Enter> as
	  another method to send a message in the Send Message dialog.

2002-05-17 22:26  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.35): Quick check for a zero time in the message
	  database.  If found, fill in with current time and print out a
	  warning.

2002-05-17 21:14  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.34): Only cause a Send Message dialog update on the
	  first ack.  Subsequent ack's cause no update.

2002-05-17 18:37  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.33): Update message windows only when the first
	  message or the first ack comes in, or when the message doesn't match
	  the same sequence number message already stored.  This helps to
	  reduce flashing of the messages windows due to multiple copies of
	  ack's/messages being received.

2002-05-17 07:01  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.32): Changes to eliminate dupes in Send Message
	  dialog.  Also changes to keep the message sequence more normal.

2002-05-16 23:29  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.31), src/interface.c (1.13): Fixes for reverse video
	  instantly on sending a message, before it's acked.

2002-05-16 22:35  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.30): Messaging fixes.  Outstanding packets are now
	  reverse video.

2002-05-16 21:47  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.29), src/db.h (1.3), src/messages.c (1.7): The start
	  of visual indicators for unacked messages.  Not completely working
	  yet, but doesn't break functionality either.

2002-05-16 16:38  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.9), src/interface_gui.c (1.11): Fixes for Mac OS X
	  (no strptime call), and for non-linux systems.  The "Set System
	  Clock from GPS Data?" togglebutton should be grey'ed out now for
	  non-linux systems.

