	* FAQ (1.6): Changes "XASTIR" to "Xastir" to match other docs.

2002-05-09 19:34  we7u

	* configure (1.9), configure.in (1.9), xastir.spec.in (1.9): Tweaks
	  to install scripts into /usr/local/xastir/script/ directory.

2002-05-09 19:33  we7u

	* scripts/Makefile.am (1.1), scripts/Makefile.in (1.1): Adding
	  Makefiles to install scripts into /usr/local/xastir/scripts/
	  directory.

2002-05-08 20:52  we7u

	* scripts/waypoint-get.pl (1.1): Here's the companion script to
	  track-get.pl.  This one will snag all of the waypoints out of a
	  Garmin GPS and create an APRS item out of each one.  The resulting
	  file can be read in by Xastir as a log file to make the waypoints
	  appear on the map screen.

2002-05-08 19:48  we7u

	* scripts/track-get.pl (1.2): Added another message at the end.

2002-05-08 19:38  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.25), src/main.c (1.69), src/main.h (1.9): Fixes for
	  some compiler warnings, by Chris Bell, KD6ZWR.

2002-05-08 19:04  we7u

	* scripts/track-get.pl (1.1): New Perl script which can fetch the
	  tracklog from a Garmin GPS, then create a log file which can be read
	  by Xastir.  Read in the log file and you'll have a track on Xastir's
	  map screen.  Needs tweaks to Xastir in order to view more than 100
	  points of the track at a time.

2002-05-08 05:45  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.86): GNIS code fixes by Chris Bell, KD6ZWR.

2002-05-07 18:40  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.68), src/maps.h (1.5): Xastir will now do a PNG
	  snapshot every time the "Enable PNG Snapshots" button is re-enabled.
	  This beats waiting 5 minutes for the next snapshot while you're
	  experimenting with things.

