2002-04-26 17:16  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.66), src/main.h (1.8), src/xa_config.c (1.15):
	  Created a #define in main.h for enabling/disabling the "Transmit Raw
	  WX data" togglebutton.  The #define enabling this button is
	  commented out.  Most likely the only people interested in this
	  button would be people debugging code for certain Peet Bros. weather
	  stations where the raw data from them is allowed over the air by the
	  APRS spec.

