	  get additional data about a particular alert.

2002-04-17 18:36  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.26): Fix for weather alerts disappearing at
	  different zoom levels or while panning around.  The problem had to
	  do with the alert getting marked as being outside the viewport, then
	  they wouldn't be looked at again.

