2002-04-12 18:11  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.16), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.16), config/language-French.sys (1.16),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.16), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.17), config/language-Portuguese.sys (1.7),
	  config/language-Spanish.sys (1.18), src/main.c (1.56): We now
	  allow four different symbols for weather stations, but print a
	  warning if trying to use an NWS symbol.  If trying to run a weather
	  station with a different symbol, the software will set the symbol to
	  the standard weather symbol automatically.

