	  changes to add tenth/hundredth rain gauge types to the weather
	  interfaces.  This is to support the two types of rain gauges for
	  Peet Brothers weather stations.  This patch implements a global
	  variable and the interface widgets needed to manipulate it, but does
	  _not_ implement the code to do anything with the variable yet.

