	* src/alert.c (1.3): There were several strncpy's without a
	  following str[last] = `\0` statement.  One of them caused a
	  segfault.  This whole file probably needs looking over for such
	  problems.  I fixed a few I thought need the statement or in the case
	  of some memmove's, seemed wrong to me.

