	* src/main.c (1.20): Added calls to TrackMouse for the map-moving
	  key events so that the position status line gets updated.

2002-03-28 18:27  francais1

	* src/main.c (1.19): Commented out code that clears mouse pointer
	  location status line when we leave Xastir window because I believe
	  we may be trying to write down that information in another window or
	  some such action.

2002-03-28 00:54  francais1

	* src/db.c (1.11), src/main.c (1.18), src/util.c (1.9),
	  src/xastir.h (1.2): Added and enabled DDMMSS coordinate format.

