	* config/tnc-startup.kpc3 (1.5): More tweaks to the kpc3 startup
	  file by we7u.

2002-03-19 06:00  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.pico (1.7): A few more pico changes by we7u.

2002-03-19 05:41  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.aea (1.2), config/tnc-startup.sys (1.4): Added
	  "echo off" to two tnc startup files.  This prevents echo'ed commands
	  from showing up in the middle of tnc data.

