	* src/maps.c (1.9): Fixing some segfaults that can occur in the
	  geoTIFF code if certain TIFF tags aren't present in the image.
	  Thanks to Derrick J. Brashear for pointing this out.  I used his
	  patch with modifications.

2002-03-11 23:36  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.kam (1.3), config/tnc-startup.kpc3 (1.3),
	  config/tnc-startup.sys (1.3): Changed "mfilter off" to "filter
	  off" for kam and kpc3.  Added "filter off" to tnc-startup.sys as
	  well.  Both mfilter and filter are in that file, making it work for
	  both types of TNC's.

