	* config/tnc-startup.kam (1.2), config/tnc-startup.kpc3 (1.2),
	  config/tnc-startup.sys (1.2): Adding "mfilter off" to most tnc
	  startup files.

2002-03-11 09:17  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.12): Increased inter-character delay to 25ms.
	  PicoPacket doesn't work with 20ms.  This is only for writes on
	  serial port TNC's.

2002-03-11 08:06  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.pico (1.5): Fullduplex not recognized by my
	  PicoPacket.  Fulldup is.

2002-03-11 07:39  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.11): Moved character write pacing to the
	  proper routine.

