	* src/interface.c (1.10), src/main.c (1.12), src/main.h (1.4):
	  Setuid patches by Jack Twilley.  Serial port throttling by we7u.

2002-03-08 22:48  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.6): Fix for Xastir blowing up when
	  changing properties on a serial TNC interface.

2002-03-07 23:33  we7u

	* config/Makefile.in (1.2): Adding PicoPacket startup file.

2002-03-07 23:31  we7u

	* Makefile.in (1.3): Adding backslash back in at the appropriate
	  point.

2002-03-07 23:30  we7u

	* acconfig.h (1.2), config.h.in (1.4), configure (1.7): Fixes for
	  warning when running autoheader.

2002-03-07 23:03  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.pico (1.4): A few more tweaks to the
	  picopacket startup file.

2002-03-07 20:58  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.8): Changed a few variables to globals.  This is to
	  allow two different GPS sentences to update the current info, then
	  perform a screen update using the combined data.  Fixed the code so
	  that receipt of one valid GPS sentence doesn't disable decoding of
	  the next.

2002-03-07 20:49  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.pico (1.3): Swapped the order of the GPS
	  string captures.

2002-03-07 20:49  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.9): Added some debugging statements.

2002-03-07 18:56  we7u

	* config/tnc-startup.pico (1.2): Proper commands for a Pico.
	  Tested.

2002-03-07 18:55  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.8): Added a delay after sending each init
	  string to a serial TNC.  This is needed to allow the TNC enough time
	  to process the command before sending the next.

2002-03-07 16:58  we7u

	* Makefile.am (1.4): Adding a backslash that was erroneously
	  deleted from Makefile.am.  Thanks to Jack Twilley for pointing this
	  out.

2002-03-07 01:02  we7u

	* config/Makefile.am (1.2), config/tnc-startup.pico (1.1): Added a
	  startup file for a Paccomm PicoPacket.

2002-03-06 23:58  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.7): Setting the time from GPS data now requires only
	  that a $GPRMC string be received, the OS be Linux, and that the
	  Xastir binary must be SUID root.  It no longer requires the $GPGGA
	  sentence to set the time.

2002-03-06 21:57  we7u

	* config/language-Dutch.sys (1.4), config/language-English.sys
	  (1.4), config/language-French.sys (1.4),
	  config/language-German.sys (1.4), config/language-Italian.sys
	  (1.4), config/language-Spanish.sys (1.4), src/main.c (1.11):
	  Changed 20 & 10 second GPS update rates down to 15 & 5.

2002-03-06 21:13  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.8): Added station trails for the local station.
	  Improved station/trail update rate for Track-Me mode.

2002-03-06 19:48  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.7): Added the capability to track ourselves.  Uses
	  the Track Station facility, so the map moves when we get too near
	  the edge of the viewport.

2002-03-06 18:11  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.5): Added a missing mutex unlock that was
	  preventing getting to the properties dialog for the new interface
	  type.

2002-03-06 09:52  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.6): Blanking out fields for which we don't have
	  actual data values.

2002-03-06 09:44  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.7): Added else clause s.t. it changes the type
	  to "aprs data" if the nmea tests fail.

2002-03-06 09:29  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.6): A few small tweaks to tnc_get_data_type().
	  Wasn't detecting NMEA data properly.

2002-03-06 09:17  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.5): Updating local position after decoding each
	  GPRMC or GPGGA string.

2002-03-06 09:03  we7u

	* src/gps.c (1.4): Now updates local position when either $GPRMC or
	  $GPGGA are received.  Both are not required except for setting time.
	  Added #ifdef __linux__ around the settime call.

2002-03-06 08:30  we7u

	* src/interface.c (1.5): Modified tnc_get_data_type() function so
	  that it doesn't call the decode_ax25_line() function.  The latter
	  function is destructive to its first parameter, which is the APRS
	  packet.  It was causing the packet to be destroyed before it could
	  be parsed and added to the database.

2002-03-06 08:27  we7u

	* src/db.c (1.6): Corrected spelling error in debug output.

2002-03-06 08:25  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.10): Added a couple of comments.

2002-03-06 07:53  we7u

	* src/interface_gui.c (1.4): Added "Set Time" button to two more
	  GPS interfaces.  Took it away from the "Serial TNC" interface.

2002-03-06 06:42  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.9): Widening the debug_level form to handle up to
	  debug level 2047.

2002-03-05 21:28  we7u

	* AUTHORS (1.4), DEBUG_LEVELS (1.2), Makefile.am (1.3), README.1ST
	  (1.7), acinclude.m4 (1.2), config.guess (1.3), config.sub (1.4),
