	  resizing shortly after.

2002-02-15 23:55  we7u

	* src/maps.c (1.5): Fixed Shapefile maps so that they work with
	  more shapefiles.  Unknown shapes are drawn in black just like the
	  roads.  Lakes shapefiles have to start with "lk" in the filename now
	  to be recognized and drawn as blue lakes.

2002-02-15 20:49  we7u

	* src/main.c (1.4): Reordering the management of the appshell popup
	  in an attempt to get rid of the bug:  "Shell widget has zero width
	  or height" that occurs on some systems.

2002-02-14 22:37  we7u

	* src/xa_config.c (1.3): Changing default greying out of stations
	  from 120 minutes down to 80 minutes.  This works better for some of
	  the satellites we can use for APRS, per Bob Bruninga's
	  recommendations.

